<div class="grid gap-3">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-950">Overview</h2>
    <p class="leading-7 text-stone-600">This tab is the default selected partial. It is rendered by <code class="rounded bg-stone-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm text-stone-900">{{ "{{ selection }}" }}</code> when no selection header is present.</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-600">
        <li>The page shell remains stable.</li>
        <li>The content panel is server-rendered.</li>
        <li>The active tab is derived from the request selection.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
